1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,260
A loss today could have meant, quite possibly, the end of everything.

2
00:00:05,260 --> 00:00:06,820
Including the Copa del rey.

3
00:00:06,820 --> 00:00:09,120
Brilliant from Sergio Roberto in midfield.

4
00:00:09,120 --> 00:00:11,440
A rapid counter-attack here, this looks dangerous.

5
00:00:11,440 --> 00:00:13,880
Five against three on the left-hand side.

6
00:00:13,880 --> 00:00:16,080
It’s a chance for Luis Suárez.

7
00:00:16,080 --> 00:00:18,060
Or it’s Gomes, Gomes with the ball.

8
00:00:18,060 --> 00:00:19,840
A pass, and it’s a shot!

9
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:32,700
Oh my word, what a moment!

10
00:00:37,480 --> 00:00:44,920
With Messi on the pitch, there’s no need to worry, no need at all, Messi’s got this!

11
00:00:52,580 --> 00:00:55,580
The all-time top scorer in the history of El Classico!

12
00:00:55,580 --> 00:00:59,520
He takes it all, even in the toughest of stadiums.

13
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:01,680
Right here, at the Bernabeu .

14
00:01:01,680 --> 00:01:04,300
His favourite stadium, oh Lionel!

15
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:09,920
From Rosario, what a player!

16
00:01:11,100 --> 00:01:13,920
What a move from Sergio Roberto!

17
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:17,520
The hero of the comeback, he’s been involved in everything today.

18
00:01:17,520 --> 00:01:20,720
A brilliant pass from Jordi Alba  to Lionel Messi.

19
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:21,860
That’s his spot.

20
00:01:22,100 --> 00:01:25,980
And there’s the final whistle!

21
00:01:25,980 --> 00:01:28,080
Confirming the win for Barcelona.

22
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:33,180
Their dreams of winning the La Liga is still alive!
